{"word":"G90 - ἀδιαφθορία - adiaphthoría - ad-ee-af-thor-ee'-ah - Uncorruptness","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδιαφθορία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">adiaphthoría</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ad-ee-af-thor-ee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Uncorruptness</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆரோக்கியம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"incorruptibility, soundness, integrity: of mind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1311 - διαφθείρω - diaphtheírō - dee-af-thi'-ro/1311\">G1311</a>; <i>incorruptibleness</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>purity</i> (of doctrine): - uncorruptness.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1311/1311\">G1311</a>, <a href=\"#/G1312/1312\">G1312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2704/2704\">G2704</a>, <a href=\"#/G5256/5256\">G5256</a>, <a href=\"#/G5349/5349\">G5349</a>, <a href=\"#/G5351/5351\">G5351</a>, <a href=\"#/G861/861\">G861</a>, <a href=\"#/G862/862\">G862</a>, <a href=\"#/G90/90\">G90</a>"}]}